{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Several techniques (Dettmers et al., 2023; Hu et al., 2022; Zhao et al., 2024) have been developed to efficiently fine-tune LLMs.",
    "Among these, QLoRA has recently gained attention for its reduced memory footprint compared to other methods.",
    "Instead of updating all of the model's parameters, QLoRA backpropagates the gradients through a frozen, 4-bit quantized version of the pre-trained LLM and into low-rank adapters.",
    "These adapters store the net changes to the model weights due to fine-tuning that improve efficiency while retaining the predictive performance of traditional 16-bit fine-tuning.",
    "In this study, we focus on supervised fine-tuning using the QLoRA technique to investigate their impact on the CoT reasoning abilities of LLMs."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Several techniques (Dettmers et al., 2023; Hu et al., 2022; Zhao et al., 2024) have been developed to efficiently fine-tune LLMs."
  ]
}